            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the beef is cooking, combine the <strong>remaining soy sauce</strong> in a bowl with the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lime[s]</strong>, your <strong>fish sauce </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>– this is your <strong>Thai-style dressing</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>carrot, mooli & pink cabbage slaw mix </strong>to the <strong>Thai-style dressing </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>Thai-style slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
