            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, add it to the <strong>Thai-style slaw </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>fragrant</strong> <strong>rice salad</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1698228462447-x200.jpg",
